{"tid":2194370,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"搞得衆籌，就要有交帶：向大家報告財政及成績","createTime":"2020-09-08T12:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T06:04:42.000Z","uid":321709,"like":77,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"21f163118be4cde6170d58467a1b647b811979cc","tid":2194370,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"我哋《三投三不投》<br />\n五月尾嘅時候搞左個衆籌<br />\n有幸得各位支持<br />\n幾日内就達標：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/legcopetition/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Flegcopetition%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=e517711a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/legcopetition/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">搞得衆籌，就要有交帶</span></span><br />\n下面呢個video<br />\n係我哋嘅財政及成績報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mUabz3qouUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmUabz3qouUU&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=371948f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mUabz3qouUU</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋幫忙令<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">初選有61萬人投票</span></span><br />\n我哋喺<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">蘋果日報登左頭版廣告</span></span>，引起不少回響<br />\n我哋成功爭取<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">6區内5區有約束力初選</span></span><br />\n我哋亦幫忙<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">令到初選由大家覺得「邊有可能？」到「理所當然」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n感謝捐款嘅各位善長仁翁<br />\n希望我哋團隊無浪費到你哋嘅善心捐款<br />\n<br />\n黎緊<br />\n我哋《三投三不投》會有一個新名<br />\n畢竟原名係專爲選舉而設<br />\n我哋團隊將會多方面為大家服務<br />\n<br />\n而且，我哋正馬不停蹄準備緊下一個大project<br />\n應該好快就可以同大家宣佈<br />\n暫時賣個關子<br />\n希望大家到時繼續支持！"},{"pid":"49756ea5af0cf9adc464820eb70fc60de3f64ab1","tid":2194370,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9843f9b1a436b200601d6636d6f0ee700ee5697a","tid":2194370,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"真係好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de391c2a95b41b0c7cb97ec90a95348083ff578","tid":2194370,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"I love you so much<br />\n香港人真係唔好放棄<br />\n唔好麻木"},{"pid":"d2c84d4b7d09ca00f06a5cd95464cc31e0188b2a","tid":2194370,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"幫你推上熱門"},{"pid":"ee738c2af2585ec515e7324fbbcba133c333fc2e","tid":2194370,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:45:04.000Z","msg":"超過80名手足將於明日提堂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194337</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4506d5c9fe9b6ab33798ec2f1b4ad2c2e886c933","tid":2194370,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beac3897dc5982f7332f1f09419380474913fb9b","tid":2194370,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee738c2af2585ec515e7324fbbcba133c333fc2e","tid":2194370,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12